Output screenshots/output/git.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set FontFamily "JetBrainsMono Nerd Font Mono"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Type "nvim ."
Enter
Sleep 3s

# Open Neogit
Type " gg"
Sleep 2s

Screenshot screenshots/output/neogit.png

Escape
Sleep 0.5s

# Open Diffview
Type " gd"
Sleep 2s

Screenshot screenshots/output/diffview.png
Sleep 1s
